        "zh_CN": "滴滴滴——！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "送外卖的机器人在门口响起了提示音。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "总算等来了食物，肴顿时眼睛一亮，迫不及待地跳下床，向机器人跑去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "当她拎着打包袋走进房间时，却没注意到纸袋的底部不堪重负，骤然裂开了一道口子。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一个橘子从缝隙中逃脱，滚到了她的脚边。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "诶？袋子怎么破了？那是店家送的水果吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "打包袋没来得及放下，她又怕错过眼前的橘子，进退间像个被按下暂停键的机器人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我来吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就在我弯腰拾起橘子时，指尖却触到一片意外的凉意。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "低头一看，肴赤足踩在地板上，莹白的脚微微发颤，脚趾也局促地蜷缩着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "怎么不穿袜子？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "听到我的问题，她才如梦初醒般低头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "起太早，脑子晕晕乎乎就忘了穿袜子，怪不得感觉有点冷。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "某个养生专家昨天还在给我科普寒气入体的危害，结果今天就自己光着脚乱跑。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一不小心忘了嘛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-1",
        "Flag": "b-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
